## Session 014 Detailed Implementation Notes

**Bug Fix Session: Forum Post Detail "Unknown Author" Issue**

**Core Problem Identified**:
Forum post detail pages were displaying "Unknown Author" instead of actual user names (e.g., "JD Singh") due to a combination of Next.js 15+ breaking changes and data structure mismatches.

**Root Causes Discovered**:
1. **Next.js 15+ Breaking Change**: Dynamic route params became Promise-based, requiring `await params` instead of direct synchronous access
2. **Data Structure Mismatch**: API response wrapped post data in `{ post: {...} }` but component was accessing properties at the top level
3. **Null Safety Issues**: Missing optional chaining across components led to undefined property access errors

**Files Modified** (8 files):
1. `app/(dashboard)/admin/forums/[slug]/page.tsx` - Added `await params` for Next.js 15+ compatibility
2. `app/(dashboard)/volunteer/forums/[slug]/page.tsx` - Added `await params` for Next.js 15+ compatibility
3. `app/(dashboard)/member/forums/[slug]/page.tsx` - Added `await params` for Next.js 15+ compatibility
4. `app/api/forums/by-slug/[slug]/route.ts` - **NEW FILE**: Created reliable forum-by-slug endpoint
5. `components/forums/forum-detail-content.tsx` - Updated to use new by-slug endpoint
6. `components/forums/post-detail-page.tsx` - Fixed data structure access (`postDetailData.post`) + comprehensive null safety
7. `components/forums/reply-thread.tsx` - Added null safety for author properties
8. `app/api/posts/[id]/route.ts` - Added debug logging for troubleshooting

**Technical Solutions Applied**:

**1. Next.js 15+ Dynamic Route Fix**:
```typescript
// BEFORE (broken in Next.js 15+)
export default function ForumDetailPage({ params }: { params: { slug: string } }) {
  const { slug } = params;
}

// AFTER (Next.js 15+ compatible)
export default async function ForumDetailPage({ params }: { params: Promise<{ slug: string }> }) {
  const { slug } = await params;
}
```

**2. Data Structure Access Fix**:
```typescript
// BEFORE (incorrect - accessing top-level)
<h1>{postDetailData.title}</h1>
<p>{postDetailData.author?.name}</p>

// AFTER (correct - accessing nested post object)
<h1>{postDetailData.post.title}</h1>
<p>{postDetailData.post.author?.name}</p>
```

**3. Comprehensive Null Safety Pattern**:
```typescript
// ALWAYS use optional chaining for author properties
author?.name || "Unknown Author"
author?.profileImageUrl || "/default-avatar.png"
```

**4. New API Endpoint Pattern**:
Created `/api/forums/by-slug/[slug]/route.ts` for reliable forum fetching by slug instead of relying on multiple ID-based endpoints.

